msgid ""
"When option _OPT_ is selected, the value of `PT_DEPTYPE`, if defined, is "
"appended to `DEPTYPE`. `OPT_DEPTYPE_OFF` works the same, but when `OPT` is "
"_not_ selected. For example:"
